Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 那座山像活著一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅彤彤的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是瓦爾茨
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:01:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要減速了 注意點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想辦理入港手續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來給你們帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是團長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他是團長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼年輕的小夥竟然是團長…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別因為他年輕就小看他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭可是該出手時就出手的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 他是我們的團長！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好幹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近距離來看相當有魄力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 相當雄偉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這座島上 岩漿不斷從地下湧出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說流量永無止境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦爾茨這個國家正是利用它的性質
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大力發展鋼鐵產業 聞名於世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你們怎麼都在這裡發呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆呆地待著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們離開波特普利茲的時候 你還在島上吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是到處都在又到處都不在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這話好哲學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這樣就接受沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和各位談談委託的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就在這地方集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在這裡說？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因此詳細情況等之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮上的人們對從外面來的人有些神經質
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神經質嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也之後再解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多沒見過的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是瓦爾茨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不少好貨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得人很少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我說 這就是之前萬事屋說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神經質嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來向你們介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位就是委託人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是拯救了波特普利茲的騎空團的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救這話說得有點誇大其詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是確實是大家一起努力做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為了我的祖國瓦爾茨 可以助我們一臂之力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了瓦爾茨？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了國家…也就是說閣下是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是王國的特務官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特務官！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是國家的秘密情報員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請各位不要宣揚此事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委託內容好像是找人來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說要找的是和國家有關的人物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓你們找的是目前下落不明的我國君主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎卡大公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂大公…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個國家最偉大的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大公下落不明就意味著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題很嚴重啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我沒辦法公開行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國民們已經發覺大公失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很難繼續瞞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以市民們才會對我們這些外來人產生戒心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據我們的調查結果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公和帝國秘密接觸過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果此事涉及到帝國的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的行動就更加受限制了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟在外交上 凡是和帝國有關的事都得非常慎重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你們能接受這個委託
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這將會是比想像中更危險的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟關係到國家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大公也許遇到了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否接受委託需要團長你來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想接受這個委託
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我們一定能找到大公的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 我會跟隨古蘭的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺們一起把大公找出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去收集情報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 兵分兩路到城裡打聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單憑委託人的資料完全不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡可能地多問問城裡的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一個很親切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常會來鎮裡逛一逛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說他很熱衷工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒那麼嚴肅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是會突然來到鎮上過來給孩子們展示一下魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公閣下是一位手藝很好的工匠 同時也是魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一位很厲害的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都是小把戲之類就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 不是小把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔法哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說過還會表演給我們看的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是的 沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們和大公叔叔很要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他給了我花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…到底去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以毀滅世界的武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡趣味的傳言罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說大公和帝國勾結在一起在做那玩意兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 那只是傳言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 但是管不住嘴的傢伙背地裡添油加醋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為最近帝國的船經常出入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大公府那邊訂購了很多的液態鋼和赤熱礦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:42.21,Default,NTP,440,0,0,,{\fs30}liquid steel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜集一些用途不明的素材也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你也相信傳言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚大公是為了國家而工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 肯定是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個是外地人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才剛到這個國家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在遊覽城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺…俺們可不是可疑人物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在城裡的人對外來人比較神經質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個也小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來大公相當受城裡人的愛戴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公不在讓很多人都感到焦慮不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來將打聽到的情報整理到一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…大公正在收集各種東西這個傳言是最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像經常訂購某些材料和工具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人說是為了製作毀滅世界的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人說他被帝國綁架了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也不時有人看到帝國的船隻出入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來感覺這些謠言可能還真是空穴來風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公之所以失蹤是為了製作毀滅世界的武器…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還不清楚是被綁架的還是自己跟著去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他很有可能現在也還在和帝國的人搞什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這樣不是很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流傳的謠言和城裡人們的意見有出入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公如此受人愛戴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他肯定是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 我只是說可能性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我們還沒有足夠的情報來建立假設
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我們應該多調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天去城外看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 得把線索逐一確認過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連內部也全都是沙子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本似乎是個工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有人在這種地方看到大公了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點有人的跡象都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有人在跟著我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在 在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別打草驚蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從昨天在城裡就一直跟著我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我感到了輕微的魔法氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方應該使用了隱形魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔法師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是帝國的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我和卡塔莉娜以及拉卡姆在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 謝謝各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去救她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開那個孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會遭這種罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到一直跟著我們的是個小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是小孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是獨當一面的魔導士！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔導士？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們應該有我的師父…也就是大公的情報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一五一十的快都告訴我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫伊歐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們剛剛救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐 很棒的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫古蘭 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請 請多關照…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺叫碧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這蜥蜴是什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真會粘人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺不是蜥蜴！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於你剛剛說的那位師父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也是我們正在尋找的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊 因為我一直看著你們的行動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲藏起來偷看是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要偷偷摸摸的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這和大叔你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你竟然叫我大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐 我們接受了尋找大公的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你能告訴我跟蹤我們的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎卡大公是我的魔法師父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說大公的魔法只是一些小把戲而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也能使用魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是教會了我魔法的很厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來大公也是魔導士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不單單是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也很擅長髮明機械裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作了不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從他見了帝國的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就變得奇怪起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後突然就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有說 也沒告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一直在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…卻完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我在城裡看到了你們 感覺你們好像知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們聽說過他在和帝國一起製造不好的東西的傳聞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這是不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的師父根本不會去做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐很敬重大公呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你告訴我們這一切 伊歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難受吧 接下來就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事對於小孩子而言過於危…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要和你們一起去找！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 所以說很危…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經決定了！我要跟著你們一起去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來請多關照了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐 很危險啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 熊孩子真是無憂無慮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在尋找這上面記載的這些地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都是我師父經常去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些地方的話 我也都去找過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這裡沒有去過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點兒年代的採石場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有騎空艇的話是沒辦法進出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:17:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐 如果你見到大公的話打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先一巴掌打飛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你見到他不高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他什麼都不說就消失不見了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能就這樣白白了事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還有這種思考方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然也想過見到了爸爸後該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但從來沒想過要先打他一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以覺得這主意也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭的老爸出去旅行後就再也沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找到大公哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是舊採石場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偌大的地方卻空空如也呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 也看不出曾經有人的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺是個很寂寥的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算是沒找對地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到了師父的魔法氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父來過這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父！你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是什麼地方啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去像是某種研究設施
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些沒見過的設備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡好像有一種不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不清…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這裡原本是星之民所使用的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該是感到了和星晶獸有關的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們丫的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這種地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們什麼都沒有做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得我會相信你說的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不應該信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 斯特姆大人都這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這麼不可信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這兩人是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們姑且算是帝國那邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波特普利茲那件事的後續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我們只是陪同我們的僱主罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刺你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經刺了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僱主？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閒聊到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃斯特帝國最高顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七耀騎士之一 黑騎士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己過去也是代表我國的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高顧問…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是帝國最有權勢的人身邊的參謀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那種人會出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那個黑鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我的師父 扎卡大公拐到哪裡去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要問我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父被帝國搞得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是你們做了什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說 這次帝國也算是受害者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也在找大公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公這傢伙相當讓人困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主動提出要共同研究 向我們要了大量援助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果卻帶著研究成果一起失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說是大公提出的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星晶的力量和機械的融合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底打算做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星晶的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你們什麼都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你們一個忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公為了將星晶的力量植入機械
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在打露莉亞的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和我的人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機械魔獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那機械是由魔法驅動的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是師父！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是師父的魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在操縱這東西的話就肯定聽得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一聲不吭就消失了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在先離開這裡再說！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊 我是伊歐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不認識我了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我啊 師父！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 鋼鐵巨人
